---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import cigarBg from '../assets/images/cigar-lounge.png';
---

<section
  id="cigar-lounge"
  class="py-24 bg-brand-dark-wood relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      {/* Visual Content */}
      <div class="relative h-[500px] lg:h-[700px] order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-brand-gold/20 z-10"
        >
          <Image
            src={cigarBg}
            alt="Le Fumoir du Vieux Comptoir"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90 transition-transform duration-1000 hover:scale-105 hover:opacity-100"
          />
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute top-10 -right-10 w-full h-full border border-brand-bordeaux-light z-0 rounded-sm hidden lg:block"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Text Content */}
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-8 pl-0 lg:pl-12">
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-brand-gold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-4"
          >
            <span class="w-12 h-px bg-brand-gold"></span>
            Un lieu exclusif
          </h2>
          <h3
            class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-brand-cream leading-tight"
          >
            Le Fumoir à <br /><span class="text-brand-bordeaux-light italic"
              >Cigares</span
            >
          </h3>
        </div>

        <div
          class="text-brand-cream/80 space-y-6 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg"
        >
          <p>
            Échappez à l'effervescence parisienne dans notre fumoir privé. Lovés
            dans de profonds fauteuils Chesterfield sous des boiseries d'époque,
            prolongez la soirée dans un havre de paix dédié aux amateurs de
            havanes et spiritueux d'exception.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-gold mr-3 mt-1 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Cave à cigares avec humidificateur sur mesure</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-gold mr-3 mt-1 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Sélection de cognacs centenaires et whiskies rares</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-gold mr-3 mt-1 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Accès réservé, idéal pour vos rendez-vous d'affaires</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
